	   <tr><td colspan=2>Indeed, Beastlords are more Shaman and Monk than anything else, but whereas Shamans are a chain class, Beastlords, Monks and Druids are all leather classes, so this would look to be a leather armor item.&nbsp;&nbsp;Surprising that Bards can't use it though with 10cha on it!  hehe<br><br>But yeah, pretty worthless compared to some things.  Right now my monk is wearing a Thick Banded Belt, ac8 wt1.0, so this would be a nice upgrade.  The mana would be wasted, of course, and the 10cha only good for selling, but the same ac (fairly high for a belt) at half the weight would be great.  Granted, at 40 he has a long time before hunting in the new CT, and there are alot of great waist items between now and then that are better.  I expect this to be a twink item (since it is not no drop) or a part of a cha gear pack for selling things.<br>&nbsp;<br>Rahzzin Talak'har<br>41 WE Ranger of Elidor<br>Tunare server</td></tr>
